{"tid":1900350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子上網辱罵鍾南山  被中国拘留15天","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T08:34:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9aee697c82ccb9c8f52b6cd097e3231c81926f2d","tid":1900350,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"綜合中國媒體報導，中國抗擊武漢肺炎領軍人物鍾南山2月初遭一名男子在網路上辱罵，這名開罵者還帶開罵中國政府，事後被公安機關行政拘留15天。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，今年1月底至2月初，廣東省中山市檢察院發現，涂姓男子通過微信發表辱罵鍾南山、中國人民和國家的言論。<br />\n<br />\n經過追查，檢方以「民事公益訴訟案件」立案審查，公安機關裁定對涂姓男子處以行政拘留15日的處罰，相關男子同時道歉。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山是中國傳染病學權威，也是中國抗擊2019年冠狀病毒疾病（武漢肺炎）的領軍人物。2003年，他也是中國抗擊嚴重急性呼吸道症侯群（SARS）的學者，以敢言而獲得聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20200227/3959394/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20200227%2F3959394%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=6585cac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20200227/3959394/</a>"},{"pid":"e5f5a8abcd564b9d87d7e6a542d22a66f80b0c6b","tid":1900350,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"鍾南山係習近平代言人<br />\n<br />\n鬧鐘南山等於鬧習近平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sP3y4tB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsP3y4tB.jpg&h=8b0de8be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5b5d9a44b4a7fd2f4a8e4d2861679596f01cdc","tid":1900350,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"鍾南山係黨員定黨委？"},{"pid":"9da4f3c71c30088364d3be7202645c613c64123b","tid":1900350,"uid":99962,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c5b5d9a44b4a7fd2f4a8e4d2861679596f01cdc","tid":1900350,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"鍾南山係黨員定黨委？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"佢地位已經超越一般黨員"},{"pid":"a015054351cd87ad3003978a0e518a3471abd8a6","tid":1900350,"uid":